## 4. Governance Mechanisms Implemented

### ✅ Prompt-Level Guardrails

* Enforce rest days in workout plans
* Avoid extreme or unsafe fitness recommendations
* Restrict medical advice

### ✅ User Conditioning

* Beginner / Intermediate / Advanced differentiation
* Context-aware recommendations

### ✅ Safety Controls

* Disclaimers for injury-related queries
* Conservative fallback responses for risky inputs

---

