## 6. Monitoring & Metrics (Planned)

### 📊 Key Metrics

* User satisfaction score
* Plan acceptance/rejection rate
* Unsafe output flag rate

### 🔁 Feedback Loop

* Track user edits to generated plans
* Identify recurring failure patterns

