## 7. Observations & Learnings

* The model tends to prioritize user intent over safety constraints
* Prompt engineering alone is not sufficient for robust risk control
* Edge cases (e.g., injuries, extreme goals) require stricter guardrails
* Combining rule-based logic with LLM responses can improve reliability

